{"tid":1108951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老鼠安偷食賓賓 一齊唱返首一步一生先啦 一齊入嚟改歌  力已盡 比個正皮啦","createTime":"2019-04-16T06:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T07:12:32.000Z","uid":140968,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44c8e7b8ae010570ca2da49a24d33f71ad37e06e","tid":1108951,"uid":140968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"主歌部分鳩嚟 屌細力啲 <br />\n<br />\n從前是誰送我走 挽我的手<br />\n但我濕透下身 不可等候<br />\n耶撚 佢再做錯 潛龍又摩西 什麼都不夠<br />\n沿途就算摷 要摷得隱蔽<br />\n隨便摷又錫 就有車cam影低<br />\n然而誰明白佢 沒你們 所想得高貴<br />\n我想告訴你們 當叫次免費雞<br />\n誰伴我去走一步一生<br />\n嗰一次心穎好猴擒 激動熱吻<br />\n曾試過佢話唔帶dom 吹瀨錫含又啜<br />\n傳教士我始終都企穩<br />\n誰伴我去走一步一生<br />\n嗰一次心穎好猴擒 激動熱吻<br />\n還有沒有人 令我驚險又興奮<br />\n願你含 同與我這車廂內共震"},{"pid":"55cc305de7b36123d20e0c06b6d9cb4474c095d4","tid":1108951,"uid":140968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:02:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8120174209fe9d14f20748f81703d907bc4acdae","tid":1108951,"uid":140968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:02:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8bc4798c40fc37dc87dacda55be4c458fb214d9","tid":1108951,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"邊間教會？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb4e8c09d434af5eb55a313fe4c574932a54e4c","tid":1108951,"uid":140968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8bc4798c40fc37dc87dacda55be4c458fb214d9","tid":1108951,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"邊間教會？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"一齊改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df65e9f7b87b1e631a9a30384b1a87f59619d83","tid":1108951,"uid":140968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"676404b705ea200a2e91adadfbf2cdf204e12